I"S<p>From Plaster to Bronze is a documentary film on the bronze-casting process of Lord Mountbatten. Directed and filmed by <a href="http://rq-art.com/about-rhea-quien/from-plaster-to-bronze/">Rhea Quien</a> in the <a href="http://www.bronzeage.co.uk/">Bronze Age Sculpture Casting Foundry</a>, London, narrated by <a href="https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0373550/">Richard Heffer</a>.</p>

